<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px;">
    <h2 style="color: #333;">Welcome to ShopFlow, {{name}}!</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Please verify your email address to activate your account:</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" 
           style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
           Verify Email Address
        </a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999;">This link will expire in 24 hours. If you did not create an account, please ignore this email.</p>
</div>
